><div class="t md6 x71 h24 yb51 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m160 x61 h24 y1d63 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What are we admonished to do that we may be </div><div class="t m9b7 x3 h24 y17a7 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kept steadfast? Luke 21: 36. </div><div class="t md9 x71 h24 y18d4 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m5f0 x61 h24 y1cb8 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What warning is given against seeking after the </div><div class="t me9a x3 h24 y1668 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">riches of this world ? 1 Tim. 6 : 9-11. Compare 1 John </div><div class="t m10ed x3 h24 y1858 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2 : 15, 16. </div><div class="t mc8 x71 h24 y196b ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m69c x64 h24 y1128 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What example is recorded as a warning? 2 Tim. </div><div class="t m141a xbd h24 y20af ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4 : 9, 10. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
